{"tid":2294374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強制用安心出行？ 跟本係支共全民監控","createTime":"2020-11-21T03:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T15:42:07.000Z","uid":183758,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"82aadd8f110cf5025054c714c3291271fdaa8f7a","tid":2294374,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:36:20.000Z","msg":"係Google Play Store 搵唔到《安心出行》只搵到&quot;LeaveHomeSafe&quot;，對於政府咁唔愛國，覺得好唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n不過政府好關心市民，睇下要求既permissions.<br />\n<br />\nThis app has access to:<br />\n📷Device &amp; app history<br />\nretrieve running apps (睇下你行緊乜嘢app)<br />\n📷Photos/Media/Files<br />\nread the contents of your USB storage (睇下你電話有乜嘢檔案)<br />\nmodify or delete the contents of your USB storage (幫你delete 不良檔案）<br />\n📷Storage<br />\nread the contents of your USB storage<br />\nmodify or delete the contents of your USB storage<br />\n📷Camera<br />\ntake pictures and videos （幫你影相，要影QR code 嘛）<br />\n📷Wi-Fi connection information<br />\nview Wi-Fi connections （唔止想要知你有無駁Internet, 重想知你駁住乜嘢Wifi）<br />\nOther<br />\nreceive data from Internet<br />\nview network connections （當然想知你用緊345G 定Wifi 定有無用緊VPN)<br />\nallow Wi-Fi Multicast reception (政府重識得親切地發multicast packet, 智慧燈柱？）<br />\nfull network access<br />\nrun at startup （boot 機就啟動，驚你唔記得開）<br />\ncontrol vibration<br />\nprevent device from sleeping<br />\nGoogle Play license check<br />\n<br />\n轉貼之前個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a3c74bc35d28cdd41af820745c327ffdb930b5","tid":2294374,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5384f464c03c9887e145b787ea6412fd5974475",